<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Archelyfiles</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffafbd, #ffc3a0); /* Gradient warna yang cerah */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: popIn 0.5s ease;
            max-width: 400px; /* Batas lebar maksimum */
            width: 90%; /* Responsif untuk layar kecil */
        }

        @keyframes popIn {
            from {
                transform: scale(0.5);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 2em;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.5; /* Menambah jarak antar baris */
        }

        a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Responsif untuk layar lebih kecil */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h2 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            .icon {
                font-size: 40px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" role="main">
        <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">ðŸŽ‰</div>
        <h2>Selamat Datang di Archelyfiles</h2>
        <p>
            Mari kita jaga setiap momen<br>
            setiap file ada petualangan, dan setiap arsip ada kenangan yang terjaga
        </p>
        <a href="/auth/login" aria-label="Login ke Archelyfiles">Login</a> | 
        <a href="/auth/register" aria-label="Daftar ke Archelyfiles">Register</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
